      <unittitle encodinganalog="245">Council About Parochiaid records <unitdate type="inclusive" encodinganalog="245$f" normal="1970/1978">1970-1978</unitdate></unittitle>
      <abstract>Michigan organization formed to oppose public aid to non-public schools and students, variously known as CAP, and the Council Against Parochiaid. Minutes of meetings, correspondence, and other materials relating to their support of Proposal C in the Michigan election of 1970, and their opposition to Proposal H (the Voucher Plan) in the election of 1978.</abstract>
